            Based in San Diego, Calif., Girard Securities Inc. is a financial company offering investment management and advisory services. The company is registered with Securities and Exchange Commission, operating under Financial Industry Regulatory Authority (FINRA). Its array of services includes traditional retail securities, insurance products/ services, fixed income and corporate finance consultation, to name a few. Girard Securities Inc. also offers various related products under partnership with different financial companies, including load and no-load mutual funds, variable and fixed annuities, term, whole, universal and variable life insurance, general securities/ options, retirement and education plans. The company also offers advisory services on a Girard Asset Managed Account platform (GAMA) and on separately managed accounts on multiple platforms.
          






















